073c5c4b-e4a4-4f62-88e7-2278e978cbf7	ca86f924-9b0c-4b32-8ab3-6e18faf54a41	\N	HTML ╨╜╨╡╨╜╤Ц ╨▒╤Ц╨╗╨┤╤Ц╤А╨╡╨┤╤Ц ╨╢╙Щ╨╜╨╡ ╨▒╤А╨░╤Г╨╖╨╡╤А ╥Ы╨░╨╗╨░╨╣ ╨╢╥▒╨╝╤Л╤Б ╤Ц╤Б╤В╨╡╨╣╨┤╤Ц?	# HTML тАФ ╨Т╨╡╨▒ ╨▒╨╡╤В╤В╤Ц╥г ╨╜╨╡╨│╤Ц╨╖╤Ц\n\nHTML (HyperText Markup Language) тАФ ╨▓╨╡╨▒ ╨▒╨╡╤В╤В╤Ц╥г ╥Ы╥▒╤А╤Л╨╗╤Л╨╝╤Л╨╜ ╤Б╨╕╨┐╨░╤В╤В╨░╨╣╤В╤Л╨╜ ╤В╤Ц╨╗. ╨Ю╨╗ "╨╢╨░╨┐╤Б╤Л╤А╨╝╨░╨╗╨░╤А" (╤В╨╡╨│╤В╨╡╤А) ╨░╤А╥Ы╤Л╨╗╤Л ╨╢╥▒╨╝╤Л╤Б ╤Ц╤Б╤В╨╡╨╣╨┤╤Ц.\n\n## ╨С╤А╨░╤Г╨╖╨╡╤А ╥Ы╨░╨╗╨░╨╣ ╨╢╥▒╨╝╤Л╤Б ╤Ц╤Б╤В╨╡╨╣╨┤╤Ц?\n\n1. ╨б╤Ц╨╖ ╨▒╤А╨░╤Г╨╖╨╡╤А╨│╨╡ URL ╤В╨╡╤А╨╡╤Б╨║╤Ц╨╖╤Б╤Ц╨╖ (╨╝╤Л╤Б╨░╨╗╤Л: google.com)\n2. ╨С╤А╨░╤Г╨╖╨╡╤А ╤Б╨╡╤А╨▓╨╡╤А╨│╨╡ HTTP ╤Б╥▒╤А╨░╨╜╤Л╤Б ╨╢╤Ц╨▒╨╡╤А╨╡╨┤╤Ц\n3. ╨б╨╡╤А╨▓╨╡╤А HTML ╤Д╨░╨╣╨╗╤Л╨╜ ╥Ы╨░╨╣╤В╨░╤А╨░╨┤╤Л\n4. ╨С╤А╨░╤Г╨╖╨╡╤А HTML-╨┤╤Ц ╨╛╥Ы╤Л╨┐, DOM (Document Object Model) ╨░╥У╨░╤И╤Л╨╜ ╨╢╨░╤Б╨░╨╣╨┤╤Л\n5. CSS-╤В╤Ц ╥Ы╨╛╨╗╨┤╨░╨╜╤Л╨┐, ╨▒╨╡╤В╤В╤Ц╥г ╤Б╤Л╤А╤В╥Ы╤Л ╤В╥п╤А╤Ц╨╜ ╥Ы╨░╨╗╤Л╨┐╤В╨░╤Б╤В╤Л╤А╨░╨┤╤Л\n6. JavaScript-╤В╤Ц ╤Ц╤Б╨║╨╡ ╥Ы╨╛╤Б╤Л╨┐, ╨▒╨╡╤В╤В╤Ц╥г ╙й╨╖╨░╤А╨░ ╔Щ╤А╨╡╨║╨╡╤В╤Ц╨╜ ╥Ы╨░╨╝╤В╨░╨╝╨░╤Б╤Л╨╖ ╨╡╤В╨╡╨┤╤Ц\n\n## ╨Х╥г ╥Ы╨░╤А╨░╨┐╨░╨╣╤Л╨╝ HTML ╨▒╨╡╤В╤Ц\n\n```html\n<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang="kk">\n  <head>\n    <meta charset="UTF-8">\n    <title>╨Ь╨╡╨╜╤Ц╥г ╨▒╨╡╤В╤Ц╨╝</title>\n  </head>\n  <body>\n    <h1>╨б╙Щ╨╗╨╡╨╝, ╨Ф╥п╨╜╨╕╨╡!</h1>\n    <p>╨С╥▒╨╗ ╨╝╨╡╨╜╤Ц╥г ╨▒╤Ц╤А╤Ц╨╜╤И╤Ц ╨▓╨╡╨▒-╨▒╨╡╤В╤Ц╨╝.</p>\n  </body>\n</html>\n```\n\n## ╨Ь╨░╥г╤Л╨╖╨┤╤Л ╤В╨╡╤А╨╝╨╕╨╜╨┤╨╡╤А\n\n| ╨в╨╡╤А╨╝╨╕╨╜ | ╨Ь╨░╥У╤Л╨╜╨░╤Б╤Л |\n|--------|---------|\n| `<!DOCTYPE html>` | HTML5 ╤Б╤В╨░╨╜╨┤╨░╤А╤В╤Л╨╜ ╤Е╨░╨▒╨░╤А╨╗╨░╨╣╨┤╤Л |\n| `<html>` | ╨С╨░╤А╨╗╤Л╥Ы ╨╝╨░╨╖╨╝╥▒╨╜╨┤╤Л ╥Ы╨░╨╝╤В╨╕╨┤╤Л |\n| `<head>` | ╨С╨╡╤В ╤В╤Г╤А╨░╨╗╤Л ╨╝╨╡╤В╨░-╨░╥Ы╨┐╨░╤А╨░╤В |\n| `<body>` | ╨С╨╡╤В╤В╨╡ ╨║╙й╤А╤Ц╨╜╨╡╤В╤Ц╨╜ ╨╝╨░╨╖╨╝╥▒╨╜ |\n\n## ╨в╨╡╨│ ╤Б╨╕╨╜╤В╨░╨║╤Б╨╕╤Б╤Ц\n\n```html\n<tagname attribute="value">╨╝╨░╨╖╨╝╥▒╨╜</tagname>\n```\n\n╨Р╤И╤Л╨╗╨░╤В╤Л╨╜ ╤В╨╡╨│: `<p>`\n╨Ц╨░╨▒╤Л╨╗╨░╤В╤Л╨╜ ╤В╨╡╨│: `</p>`\n╙и╨╖╨┤╤Ц╨│╤Ц╨╜╨╡╨╜ ╨╢╨░╨▒╤Л╨╗╨░╤В╤Л╨╜ ╤В╨╡╨│: `<img src="photo.jpg" />`\n\n## ╨Ъ╨╡╥г╨╡╤Б\n\n╨С╨░╤А╨╗╤Л╥Ы HTML ╤Д╨░╨╣╨╗╨┤╨░╤А `.html` ╨║╨╡╥г╨╡╨╣╤В╤Ц╨╝╤Ц╨╝╨╡╨╜ ╤Б╨░╥Ы╤В╨░╨╗╨░╨┤╤Л. ╨С╨░╤Б╤В╨░╨┐╥Ы╤Л ╤Д╨░╨╣╨╗ ╙Щ╨┤╨╡╤В╤В╨╡ `index.html` ╨┤╨╡╨┐ ╨░╤В╨░╨╗╨░╨┤╤Л тАФ ╨▒╥▒╨╗ ╨▒╤А╨░╤Г╨╖╨╡╤А ╨▒╤Ц╤А╤Ц╨╜╤И╤Ц ╤Ц╨╖╨┤╨╡╨╣╤В╤Ц╨╜ ╤Д╨░╨╣╨╗.	\N	╨в╨░╨┐╤Б╤Л╤А╨╝╨░: ╨Ь╤Л╨╜╨░ HTML ╨║╨╛╨┤╤Л╨╜╨┤╨░╥У╤Л ╨▒╨╛╤Б ╨╛╤А╤Л╨╜╨┤╤Л ╤В╨╛╨╗╤В╤Л╤А╤Л╥г╤Л╨╖.\n╨Т╨╡╨▒ ╨▒╨╡╤В╤В╤Ц╥г ╨╜╨╡╨│╤Ц╨╖╨│╤Ц ╨╝╨░╨╖╨╝╥▒╨╜╤Л ╥Ы╨░╨╜╨┤╨░╨╣ ╤В╨╡╨│╨║╨╡ ╨╛╤А╨╜╨░╨╗╨░╤Б╨░╨┤╤Л?\n\n<html>\n  <head>...</head>\n  <___>╨Ь╨░╨╖╨╝╥▒╨╜ ╨╛╤Б╤Л╨╜╨┤╨░</___>\n</html>\n\n╨в╨╡╨║ ╤В╨╡╨│ ╨░╤В╨░╤Г╤Л╨╜ ╨╢╨░╨╖╤Л╥г╤Л╨╖ (╨╝╤Л╤Б╨░╨╗╤Л: body)	body	1	2026-03-03 20:34:17.903
09816216-2072-4740-ba58-0d1f92872624	ca86f924-9b0c-4b32-8ab3-6e18faf54a41	\N	HTML ╤В╨╡╨│╤В╨╡╤А╤Ц: ╤В╨░╥Ы╤Л╤А╤Л╨┐╤В╨░╤А, ╨┐╨░╤А╨░╨│╤А╨░╤Д╤В╨░╤А, ╤Б╤Ц╨╗╤В╨╡╨╝╨╡╨╗╨╡╤А	# ╨Э╨╡╨│╤Ц╨╖╨│╤Ц HTML ╤В╨╡╨│╤В╨╡╤А╤Ц\n\n## ╨в╨░╥Ы╤Л╤А╤Л╨┐ ╤В╨╡╨│╤В╨╡╤А╤Ц (h1тАУh6)\n\n╨в╨░╥Ы╤Л╤А╤Л╨┐╤В╨░╤А SEO ╥п╤И╤Ц╨╜ ╨╝╨░╥г╤Л╨╖╨┤╤Л. `h1` тАФ ╨╡╥г ╨╝╨░╥г╤Л╨╖╨┤╤Л, `h6` тАФ ╨╡╥г ╨░╨╖ ╨╝╨░╥г╤Л╨╖╨┤╤Л.\n\n```html\n<h1>╨С╨╡╤В╨░╨╜╨░╨╗╤Л╥Ы ╤В╨░╥Ы╤Л╤А╤Л╨┐</h1>\n<h2>╨С╙й╨╗╤Ц╨╝ ╤В╨░╥Ы╤Л╤А╤Л╨▒╤Л</h2>\n<h3>╨Ъ╤Ц╤И╤Ц ╨▒╙й╨╗╤Ц╨╝</h3>\n```\n\n**╨Х╤А╨╡╨╢╨╡:** ╨С╤Ц╤А ╨▒╨╡╤В╤В╨╡ ╤В╨╡╨║ ╨С╨Ж╨а `<h1>` ╨▒╨╛╨╗╤Г╤Л ╤В╨╕╤Ц╤Б.\n\n## ╨Я╨░╤А╨░╨│╤А╨░╤Д ╤В╨╡╨│╤Ц\n\n```html\n<p>╨С╥▒╨╗ ╨┐╨░╤А╨░╨│╤А╨░╤Д ╨╝╙Щ╤В╤Ц╨╜╤Ц. ╨С╤А╨░╤Г╨╖╨╡╤А ╨░╨▓╤В╨╛╨╝╨░╤В╤В╤Л ╤В╥п╤А╨┤╨╡ ╨╢╨╛╨╗ ╥п╨╖╤Ц╤Б╤Ц╨╜ ╥Ы╨╛╤Б╨░╨┤╤Л.</p>\n<p>╨Х╨║╤Ц╨╜╤И╤Ц ╨┐╨░╤А╨░╨│╤А╨░╤Д.</p>\n```\n\n## ╨б╤Ц╨╗╤В╨╡╨╝╨╡ ╤В╨╡╨│╤Ц (anchor)\n\n```html\n<!-- ╨б╤Л╤А╤В╥Ы╤Л ╤Б╤Ц╨╗╤В╨╡╨╝╨╡ -->\n<a href="https://google.com" target="_blank">Google-╨│╨╡ ╙й╤В╤Г</a>\n\n<!-- ╨Ж╤И╨║╤Ц ╤Б╤Ц╨╗╤В╨╡╨╝╨╡ -->\n<a href="/about.html">╨С╤Ц╨╖ ╤В╤Г╤А╨░╨╗╤Л</a>\n\n<!-- ╨С╨╡╤В ╤Ц╤И╤Ц╨╜╨┤╨╡╨│╤Ц ╤П╨║╨╛╤А -->\n<a href="#contact">╨С╨░╨╣╨╗╨░╨╜╤Л╤Б</a>\n```\n\n**`target="_blank"`** тАФ ╤Б╤Ц╨╗╤В╨╡╨╝╨╡╨╜╤Ц ╨╢╨░╥г╨░ ╥Ы╨╛╨╣╤Л╨╜╨┤╤Л╨┤╨░ ╨░╤И╨░╨┤╤Л.\n\n## ╨Ь╙Щ╤В╤Ц╨╜ ╨┐╤Ц╤И╤Ц╨╝╨┤╨╡╤Г\n\n```html\n<strong>╥Ъ╨░╨╗╤Л╥г ╨╝╙Щ╤В╤Ц╨╜</strong>   <!-- ╨╝╨░╥г╤Л╨╖╨┤╤Л -->\n<em>╨Ъ╤Г╤А╤Б╨╕╨▓ ╨╝╙Щ╤В╤Ц╨╜</em>          <!-- ╨╡╨║╨┐╤Ц╨╜ -->\n<br>                            <!-- ╨╢╨╛╨╗ ╥п╨╖╤Ц╤Б╤Ц -->\n<hr>                            <!-- ╨║╙й╨╗╨┤╨╡╨╜╨╡╥г ╤Б╤Л╨╖╤Л╥Ы -->\n```\n\n## ╨в╤Ц╨╖╤Ц╨╝╨┤╨╡╤А\n\n```html\n<!-- ╨Э╥п╨║╤В╨╡╨╗╨╡╨╜╨│╨╡╨╜ (╤А╨╡╤В╤В╨╡╨╗╨╝╨╡╨│╨╡╨╜) -->\n<ul>\n  <li>╨Р╨╗╨╝╨░</li>\n  <li>╨С╨░╨╜╨░╨╜</li>\n</ul>\n\n<!-- ╨Э╙й╨╝╤Ц╤А╨╗╨╡╨╜╨│╨╡╨╜ (╤А╨╡╤В╤В╨╡╨╗╨│╨╡╨╜) -->\n<ol>\n  <li>╨С╤Ц╤А╤Ц╨╜╤И╤Ц ╥Ы╨░╨┤╨░╨╝</li>\n  <li>╨Х╨║╤Ц╨╜╤И╤Ц ╥Ы╨░╨┤╨░╨╝</li>\n</ol>\n```\n\n## ╨в╙Щ╨╢╤Ц╤А╨╕╨▒╨╡ ╨╢╨░╤Б╨░╥г╤Л╨╖\n\nVS Code-╤В╨╡ `index.html` ╤Д╨░╨╣╨╗ ╨╢╨░╤Б╨░╥г╤Л╨╖, `!` ╤В╨╡╤А╤Ц╨┐, Tab ╨▒╨░╤Б╤Л╥г╤Л╨╖ тАФ ╨░╨▓╤В╨╛╤В╨╛╨╗╤В╤Л╤А╤Г ╨║╨╛╨┤╤В╤Л ╨╢╨░╤Б╨░╨╣╨┤╤Л!	\N	╨в╨░╨┐╤Б╤Л╤А╨╝╨░: ╨Ь╤Л╨╜╨░ HTML-╨┤╨╡ ╥Ы╨░╨╜╨┤╨░╨╣ ╤В╨╡╨│ ╨╢╨╡╤В╤Ц╤Б╨┐╨╡╨╣╨┤╤Ц?\n\n<ol>\n  <___>╨С╤Ц╤А╤Ц╨╜╤И╤Ц ╥Ы╨░╨┤╨░╨╝</___>\n  <li>╨Х╨║╤Ц╨╜╤И╤Ц ╥Ы╨░╨┤╨░╨╝</li>\n</ol>\n\n╨в╨╡╨║ ╤В╨╡╨│ ╨░╤В╨░╤Г╤Л╨╜ ╨╢╨░╨╖╤Л╥г╤Л╨╖ (╨╢╨░╤Г╨░╨┐: li)	li	2	2026-03-03 20:34:17.907
4c2c6859-6dd2-4ea4-bd55-279927922444	ca86f924-9b0c-4b32-8ab3-6e18faf54a41	\N	HTML ╤Б╤Г╤А╨╡╤В╤В╨╡╤А, ╨║╨╡╤Б╤В╨╡╨╗╨╡╤А, ╨┐╤Ц╤И╤Ц╨╝╨┤╨╡╤А	# ╨Ь╨╡╨┤╨╕╨░ ╨╢╙Щ╨╜╨╡ ╨┤╨╡╤А╨╡╨║╤В╨╡╤А ╤В╨╡╨│╤В╨╡╤А╤Ц\n\n## ╨б╤Г╤А╨╡╤В ╤В╨╡╨│╤Ц\n\n```html\n<img src="photo.jpg" alt="╨б╤Г╤А╨╡╤В╤В╤Ц╥г ╤Б╨╕╨┐╨░╤В╤В╨░╨╝╨░╤Б╤Л" width="400" height="300">\n```\n\n- **`src`** тАФ ╤Б╤Г╤А╨╡╤В ╨╢╨╛╨╗╤Л (URL ╨╜╨╡╨╝╨╡╤Б╨╡ ╤Д╨░╨╣╨╗)\n- **`alt`** тАФ ╤Б╤Г╤А╨╡╤В ╨╢╥п╨║╤В╨╡╨╗╨╝╨╡╤Б╨╡ ╨╜╨╡╨╝╨╡╤Б╨╡ ╤Н╨║╤А╨░╨╜╨┤╤Л╥Ы ╨╛╥Ы╤Л╤А╨╝╨░╨╜ ╥п╤И╤Ц╨╜ ╨╝╙Щ╤В╤Ц╨╜\n- **`width/height`** тАФ ╙й╨╗╤И╨╡╨╝╨┤╨╡╤А (px ╨┤╨╡, % ╨┤╨╡ ╨▒╨╛╨╗╨░╨┤╤Л)\n\n## ╨Ъ╨╡╤Б╤В╨╡\n\n```html\n<table>\n  <thead>\n    <tr>\n      <th>╨Р╤В╤Л</th>\n      <th>╨Ц╨░╤Б╤Л</th>\n    </tr>\n  </thead>\n  <tbody>\n    <tr>\n      <td>╨Р╨╗╨╕╨▒╨╡╨║</td>\n      <td>25</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td>╨Р╨╣╨│╨╡╤А╤Ц╨╝</td>\n      <td>22</td>\n    </tr>\n  </tbody>\n</table>\n```\n\n| ╨в╨╡╨│ | ╨Ь╨░╥У╤Л╨╜╨░╤Б╤Л |\n|-----|---------|\n| `<table>` | ╨Ъ╨╡╤Б╤В╨╡ ╨║╨╛╨╜╤В╨╡╨╣╨╜╨╡╤А╤Ц |\n| `<thead>` | ╨в╨░╥Ы╤Л╤А╤Л╨┐ ╨╢╨╛╨╗╨┤╨░╤А╤Л |\n| `<tbody>` | ╨Э╨╡╨│╤Ц╨╖╨│╤Ц ╨┤╨╡╤А╨╡╨║╤В╨╡╤А |\n| `<tr>` | ╨Ъ╨╡╤Б╤В╨╡ ╨╢╨╛╨╗╤Л (Table Row) |\n| `<th>` | ╨в╨░╥Ы╤Л╤А╤Л╨┐ ╥▒╤П╤И╤Л╥У╤Л (Table Header) |\n| `<td>` | ╨Ф╨╡╤А╨╡╨║╤В╨╡╤А ╥▒╤П╤И╤Л╥У╤Л (Table Data) |\n\n## ╨Я╤Ц╤И╤Ц╨╝ (Form)\n\n```html\n<form method="post" action="/submit">\n  <label for="name">╨Р╤В╤Л-╨╢╙й╨╜╤Ц:</label>\n  <input type="text" id="name" name="name" placeholder="╨Р╤В╤Л╥г╤Л╨╖╨┤╤Л ╨╡╨╜╨│╤Ц╨╖╤Ц╥г╤Ц╨╖">\n\n  <label for="email">Email:</label>\n  <input type="email" id="email" name="email">\n\n  <label for="message">╨е╨░╨▒╨░╤А╨╗╨░╨╝╨░:</label>\n  <textarea id="message" name="message" rows="4"></textarea>\n\n  <button type="submit">╨Ц╤Ц╨▒╨╡╤А╤Г</button>\n</form>\n```\n\n## input ╤В╥п╤А╨╗╨╡╤А╤Ц\n\n```html\n<input type="text">      <!-- ╨╝╙Щ╤В╤Ц╨╜ -->\n<input type="email">     <!-- email (╨▓╨░╨╗╨╕╨┤╨░╤Ж╨╕╤П ╨▒╨░╤А) -->\n<input type="password">  <!-- ╨┐╨░╤А╨╛╨╗╤М (╨╢╨░╤Б╤Л╤А╤Л╨╗╨░╨┤╤Л) -->\n<input type="number">    <!-- ╤Б╨░╨╜ -->\n<input type="checkbox">  <!-- ╤Д╨╗╨░╨╢╨╛╨║ -->\n<input type="radio">     <!-- ╨┤╙й╥г╨│╨╡╨╗╨╡╨║ ╤В╨░╥г╨┤╨░╤Г -->\n<input type="file">      <!-- ╤Д╨░╨╣╨╗ ╨╢╥п╨║╤В╨╡╤Г -->\n```	\N	╨в╨░╨┐╤Б╤Л╤А╨╝╨░: ╨Ъ╨╡╤Б╤В╨╡╨┤╨╡╨│╤Ц ╤В╨░╥Ы╤Л╤А╤Л╨┐ ╥▒╤П╤И╤Л╥У╤Л╨╜╨░ ╥Ы╨╛╨╗╨┤╨░╨╜╤Л╨╗╨░╤В╤Л╨╜ ╤В╨╡╨│ ╥Ы╨░╨╣╤Б╤Л╤Б╤Л?\n\n<table>\n  <tr>\n    <___>╨Р╤В╤Л</___>   тЖР ╤В╨░╥Ы╤Л╤А╤Л╨┐ ╥▒╤П╤И╤Л╥У╤Л\n    <td>╨Ь╙Щ╨╜╤Ц</td>    тЖР ╨┤╨╡╤А╨╡╨║╤В╨╡╤А ╥▒╤П╤И╤Л╥У╤Л\n  </tr>\n</table>\n\n╨в╨╡╨║ ╤В╨╡╨│ ╨░╤В╨░╤Г╤Л╨╜ ╨╢╨░╨╖╤Л╥г╤Л╨╖ (╨╢╨░╤Г╨░╨┐: th)	th	3	2026-03-03 20:34:17.911
f51520ab-99ad-4699-a881-1144e2e6ac45	ca86f924-9b0c-4b32-8ab3-6e18faf54a41	\N	CSS-╨║╨╡ ╨║╤Ц╤А╤Ц╤Б╨┐╨╡: ╤Б╤В╨╕╨╗╤М╨┤╨╡╤А ╥Ы╨░╨╗╨░╨╣ ╨╢╥▒╨╝╤Л╤Б ╤Ц╤Б╤В╨╡╨╣╨┤╤Ц	# CSS тАФ ╨Т╨╡╨▒ ╨С╨╡╤В╤В╤Ц╥г ╨б╤Л╤А╤В╥Ы╤Л ╨в╥п╤А╤Ц\n\nCSS (Cascading Style Sheets) тАФ HTML ╤Н╨╗╨╡╨╝╨╡╨╜╤В╤В╨╡╤А╤Ц╨╜╤Ц╥г ╤Б╤Л╤А╤В╥Ы╤Л ╤В╥п╤А╤Ц╨╜ (╤В╥п╤Б, ╙й╨╗╤И╨╡╨╝, ╨╛╤А╨╜╨░╨╗╨░╤Б╤Г) ╨░╨╜╤Л╥Ы╤В╨░╨╣╨┤╤Л.\n\n## CSS-╤В╤Ц HTML-╨│╨╡ ╥Ы╨╛╤Б╤Г╨┤╤Л╥г 3 ╨╢╨╛╨╗╤Л\n\n### 1. ╨б╤Л╤А╤В╥Ы╤Л CSS ╤Д╨░╨╣╨╗╤Л (╨╡╥г ╨╢╨░╥Ы╤Б╤Л ╤В╙Щ╤Б╤Ц╨╗)\n```html\n<head>\n  <link rel="stylesheet" href="styles.css">\n</head>\n```\n\n### 2. `<style>` ╤В╨╡╨│╤Ц ╤Ц╤И╤Ц╨╜╨┤╨╡\n```html\n<head>\n  <style>\n    p { color: blue; }\n  </style>\n</head>\n```\n\n### 3. Inline ╤Б╤В╨╕╨╗╤М (╨▒╨╛╨╗╨┤╤Л╤А╨╝╨░╥г╤Л╨╖)\n```html\n<p style="color: blue;">╨Ь╙Щ╤В╤Ц╨╜</p>\n```\n\n## CSS ╤Б╨╕╨╜╤В╨░╨║╤Б╨╕╤Б╤Ц\n\n```css\nselector {\n  property: value;\n  property: value;\n}\n```\n\n╨Ь╤Л╤Б╨░╨╗:\n```css\nh1 {\n  color: #2563eb;        /* ╤В╥п╤Б */\n  font-size: 32px;       /* ╨╝╙й╨╗╤И╨╡╤А */\n  font-weight: bold;     /* ╥Ы╨░╨╗╤Л╥г╨┤╤Л╥Ы */\n  text-align: center;    /* ╤В╤Г╤А╨░╨╗╨░╤Г */\n}\n\np {\n  color: #374151;\n  line-height: 1.6;      /* ╨╢╨╛╨╗ ╨▒╨╕╤Ц╨║╤В╤Ц╨│╤Ц */\n  max-width: 700px;      /* ╨╝╨░╨║╤Б╨╕╨╝╤Г╨╝ ╨║╨╡╥г╨┤╤Ц╨║ */\n}\n```\n\n## ╨б╨╡╨╗╨╡╨║╤В╨╛╤А╨╗╨░╤А\n\n```css\n/* ╨в╨╡╨│ ╤Б╨╡╨╗╨╡╨║╤В╨╛╤А╤Л */\np { color: gray; }\n\n/* ╨Ъ╨╗╨░╤Б╤Б ╤Б╨╡╨╗╨╡╨║╤В╨╛╤А╤Л (. ╨▒╨╡╨╗╨│╤Ц╤Б╤Ц) */\n.card { background: white; }\n\n/* ID ╤Б╨╡╨╗╨╡╨║╤В╨╛╤А╤Л (# ╨▒╨╡╨╗╨│╤Ц╤Б╤Ц) */\n#header { background: navy; }\n\n/* ╨Ъ╨╛╨╝╨▒╨╕╨╜╨░╤Ж╨╕╤П╨╗╤Л╥Ы */\n.card h2 { font-size: 20px; }  /* .card ╤Ц╤И╤Ц╨╜╨┤╨╡╨│╤Ц h2 */\n```\n\n## ╨Ь╨░╥г╤Л╨╖╨┤╤Л CSS ╥Ы╨░╤Б╨╕╨╡╤В╤В╨╡╤А╤Ц\n\n| ╥Ъ╨░╤Б╨╕╨╡╤В | ╨Ь╤Л╤Б╨░╨╗ | ╨Ь╨░╥У╤Л╨╜╨░╤Б╤Л |\n|--------|-------|---------|\n| `color` | `color: red` | ╨Ь╙Щ╤В╤Ц╨╜ ╤В╥п╤Б╤Ц |\n| `background-color` | `background-color: #fff` | ╨д╨╛╨╜ ╤В╥п╤Б╤Ц |\n| `font-size` | `font-size: 16px` | ╨Ь╙й╨╗╤И╨╡╤А |\n| `margin` | `margin: 20px` | ╨б╤Л╤А╤В╥Ы╤Л ╤И╨╡╨│╤Ц╨╜╤Ц╤Б |\n| `padding` | `padding: 10px` | ╨Ж╤И╨║╤Ц ╤И╨╡╨│╤Ц╨╜╤Ц╤Б |\n| `border` | `border: 1px solid gray` | ╨и╨╡╨║╨░╤А╨░ |\n| `width/height` | `width: 100%` | ╙и╨╗╤И╨╡╨╝ |	\N	╨в╨░╨┐╤Б╤Л╤А╨╝╨░: CSS-╤В╨╡ ╨║╨╗╨░╤Б╤Б ╨░╤В╨░╤Г╤Л╨╜ ╨▒╨╡╨╗╨│╤Ц╨╗╨╡╤Г ╥п╤И╤Ц╨╜ ╥Ы╨░╨╜╨┤╨░╨╣ ╤Б╨╕╨╝╨▓╨╛╨╗ ╥Ы╨╛╨╗╨┤╨░╨╜╤Л╨╗╨░╨┤╤Л?\n\n╨Ь╤Л╤Б╨░╨╗╤Л: .card, .btn, .header\n\n╨в╨╡╨║ ╤Б╨╕╨╝╨▓╨╛╨╗╨┤╤Л ╨╢╨░╨╖╤Л╥г╤Л╨╖ (╨╢╨░╤Г╨░╨┐: .)	.	4	2026-03-03 20:34:17.915
69d31392-28e4-4e43-8b41-0804e8b5c658	ca86f924-9b0c-4b32-8ab3-6e18faf54a41	\N	CSS Box Model: margin, padding, border	# CSS Box Model\n\n╙Ш╤А╨▒╤Ц╤А HTML ╤Н╨╗╨╡╨╝╨╡╨╜╤В тАФ ╨▒╥▒╨╗ "╥Ы╨╛╤А╨░╨┐" (box). Box Model ╥Ы╨╛╤А╨░╨┐╤В╤Л╥г ╥Ы╨░╨╗╨░╨╣ ╙й╨╗╤И╨╡╨╜╨╡╤В╤Ц╨╜╤Ц╨╜ ╨░╨╜╤Л╥Ы╤В╨░╨╣╨┤╤Л.\n\n## Box Model ╥Ы╥▒╤А╤Л╨╗╤Л╨╝╤Л\n\n```\nтФМтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФР\nтФВ           MARGIN              тФВ  тЖР ╤Б╤Л╤А╤В╥Ы╤Л ╨▒╨╛╤Б ╨║╨╡╥г╤Ц╤Б╤В╤Ц╨║\nтФВ  тФМтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФР   тФВ\nтФВ  тФВ        BORDER          тФВ   тФВ  тЖР ╤И╨╡╨║╨░╤А╨░\nтФВ  тФВ  тФМтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФР  тФВ   тФВ\nтФВ  тФВ  тФВ     PADDING      тФВ  тФВ   тФВ  тЖР ╤Ц╤И╨║╤Ц ╨▒╨╛╤Б ╨║╨╡╥г╤Ц╤Б╤В╤Ц╨║\nтФВ  тФВ  тФВ  тФМтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФР  тФВ  тФВ   тФВ\nтФВ  тФВ  тФВ  тФВ  CONTENT   тФВ  тФВ  тФВ   тФВ  тЖР ╨╝╨░╨╖╨╝╥▒╨╜\nтФВ  тФВ  тФВ  тФФтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФШ  тФВ  тФВ   тФВ\nтФВ  тФВ  тФФтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФШ  тФВ   тФВ\nтФВ  тФФтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФШ   тФВ\nтФФтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФШ\n```\n\n## ╨Ь╤Л╤Б╨░╨╗\n\n```css\n.card {\n  /* ╨Ь╨░╨╖╨╝╥▒╨╜ */\n  width: 300px;\n  height: 200px;\n\n  /* ╨Ж╤И╨║╤Ц ╤И╨╡╨│╤Ц╨╜╤Ц╤Б (╨╝╨░╨╖╨╝╥▒╨╜ ╨╝╨╡╨╜ ╤И╨╡╨║╨░╤А╨░ ╨░╤А╨░╤Б╤Л) */\n  padding: 20px;          /* ╨▒╨░╤А╨╗╤Л╥Ы ╨╢╨░╥Ы╤В╨░╨╜ */\n  padding-top: 10px;      /* ╤В╨╡╨║ ╨╢╨╛╥У╨░╤А╤Л╨┤╨░╨╜ */\n  padding: 10px 20px;     /* ╨╢╨╛╥У╨░╤А╤Л/╤В╙й╨╝╨╡╨╜ | ╨╛╥г/╤Б╨╛╨╗ */\n\n  /* ╨и╨╡╨║╨░╤А╨░ */\n  border: 2px solid #e5e7eb;\n  border-radius: 12px;    /* ╨┤╙й╥г╨│╨╡╨╗╨╡╨║╤В╨╡╨╗╨│╨╡╨╜ ╨▒╥▒╤А╤Л╤И╤В╨░╤А */\n\n  /* ╨б╤Л╤А╤В╥Ы╤Л ╤И╨╡╨│╤Ц╨╜╤Ц╤Б (╤Н╨╗╨╡╨╝╨╡╨╜╤В╤В╨╡╤А ╨░╤А╨░╤Б╤Л) */\n  margin: 16px;           /* ╨▒╨░╤А╨╗╤Л╥Ы ╨╢╨░╥Ы╤В╨░╨╜ */\n  margin: 0 auto;         /* ╤Б╨╛╨╗╨╢╨░╥Ы/╨╛╥г╨╢╨░╥Ы ╨░╨▓╤В╨╛ = ╨╛╤А╤В╨░╥У╨░ */\n}\n```\n\n## box-sizing\n\n**╨Ь╨░╥г╤Л╨╖╨┤╤Л!** ╙Ш╨┤╨╡╨┐╨║╤Ц ╨╢╨░╥У╨┤╨░╨╣╨┤╨░ `width` ╤В╨╡╨║ ╨╝╨░╨╖╨╝╥▒╨╜╨┤╤Л ╙й╨╗╤И╨╡╨╣╨┤╤Ц.\n\n```css\n/* ╨Х╤Б╨║╤Ц (╨┐╤А╨╛╨▒╨╗╨╡╨╝╨░╨╗╤Л╥Ы) ╨╢╨╛╨╗: */\n/* width: 300px + padding: 20px = ╨╢╨░╨╗╨┐╤Л 340px */\n\n/* ╨Ц╨░╥г╨░ (╥▒╤Б╤Л╨╜╤Л╨╗╨░╨┤╤Л): */\n* {\n  box-sizing: border-box;  /* width padding-╨┤╤Л ╥Ы╨╛╤Б╨░╨┤╤Л */\n}\n/* ╨Х╨╜╨┤╤Ц width: 300px = ╨╝╨░╨╖╨╝╥▒╨╜ + padding + border = 300px */\n```\n\n## display ╥Ы╨░╤Б╨╕╨╡╤В╤Ц\n\n```css\ndiv    { display: block; }    /* ╤В╨╛╨╗╤Л╥Ы ╨║╨╡╥г╨┤╤Ц╨║ ╨░╨╗╨░╨┤╤Л, ╨╢╨░╥г╨░ ╨╢╨╛╨╗╨┤╨░╨╜ */\nspan   { display: inline; }   /* ╤В╨╡╨║ ╨╝╨░╨╖╨╝╥▒╨╜ ╨║╨╡╥г╨┤╤Ц╨│╤Ц, ╨▒╤Ц╤А ╨╢╨╛╨╗╨┤╨░ */\nimg    { display: inline-block; } /* inline + width/height ╥Ы╨░╨▒╤Л╨╗╨┤╨░╨╣╨┤╤Л */\n.hide  { display: none; }     /* ╤Н╨╗╨╡╨╝╨╡╨╜╤В╤В╤Ц ╨╢╨░╤Б╤Л╤А╨░╨┤╤Л */\n```\n\n## ╨Я╤А╨░╨║╤В╨╕╨║╨░\n\nDevTools-╤В╨░ (F12) ╨║╨╡╨╖ ╨║╨╡╨╗╨│╨╡╨╜ ╤Н╨╗╨╡╨╝╨╡╨╜╤В╤В╤Ц ╤В╨░╥г╨┤╨░╥г╤Л╨╖ тАФ "Computed" ╥Ы╨╛╨╣╤Л╨╜╨┤╤Л╤Б╤Л╨╜╨┤╨░ ╨╛╨╜╤Л╥г Box Model-╤Ц╨╜ ╨║╙й╤А╤Г╨│╨╡ ╨▒╨╛╨╗╨░╨┤╤Л.	\N	╨в╨░╨┐╤Б╤Л╤А╨╝╨░: ╨н╨╗╨╡╨╝╨╡╨╜╤В╤В╨╡╤А ╨Р╨а╨Р╨б╨л╨Э╨Ф╨Р╥Т╨л ╨▒╨╛╤Б ╨║╨╡╥г╤Ц╤Б╤В╤Ц╨║╤В╤Ц ╨▒╨╡╤А╨╡╤В╤Ц╨╜ CSS ╥Ы╨░╤Б╨╕╨╡╤В╤Ц ╥Ы╨░╨╣╤Б╤Л╤Б╤Л?\n\n╨Ь╤Л╤Б╨░╨╗╤Л: div { ___: 20px; }\n\n╨в╨╡╨║ ╥Ы╨░╤Б╨╕╨╡╤В ╨░╤В╨░╤Г╤Л╨╜ ╨╢╨░╨╖╤Л╥г╤Л╨╖ (╨╢╨░╤Г╨░╨┐: margin)	margin	5	2026-03-03 20:34:17.918
08662d8c-1b58-4996-89fb-22212350f660	ca86f924-9b0c-4b32-8ab3-6e18faf54a41	\N	CSS Flexbox: ╨╖╨░╨╝╨░╨╜╨░╤Г╨╕ ╨╛╤А╨╜╨░╨╗╨░╤Б╤Г	# Flexbox тАФ ╨Ш╨║╨╡╨╝╨┤╤Ц ╨Ю╤А╨╜╨░╨╗╨░╤Б╤Г\n\nFlexbox ╤Н╨╗╨╡╨╝╨╡╨╜╤В╤В╨╡╤А╨┤╤Ц ╨╢╨╛╨╗ ╨╜╨╡╨╝╨╡╤Б╨╡ ╨▒╨░╥У╨░╨╜ ╨▒╨╛╨╣╤Л╨╜╤И╨░ ╤А╨╡╤В╤В╨╡╤Г╨┤╤Ц ╨╢╨╡╥г╤Ц╨╗╨┤╨╡╤В╨╡╨┤╤Ц.\n\n## ╨Ж╤Б╨║╨╡ ╥Ы╨╛╤Б╤Г\n\n```css\n.container {\n  display: flex;        /* flex ╨║╨╛╨╜╤В╨╡╨╣╨╜╨╡╤А ╨╢╨░╤Б╨░╨╣╨┤╤Л */\n}\n```\n\n╨Ю╤Б╤Л╨┤╨░╨╜ ╨║╨╡╨╣╤Ц╨╜ `.container` ╤Ц╤И╤Ц╨╜╨┤╨╡╨│╤Ц ╨▒╨░╤А╨╗╤Л╥Ы ╤В╤Ц╨║╨╡╨╗╨╡╨╣ ╨▒╨░╨╗╨░╨╗╨░╤А flex ╤Н╨╗╨╡╨╝╨╡╨╜╤В╤В╨╡╤А ╨▒╨╛╨╗╨░╨┤╤Л.\n\n## ╨Э╨╡╨│╤Ц╨╖╨│╤Ц ╥Ы╨░╤Б╨╕╨╡╤В╤В╨╡╤А (╨║╨╛╨╜╤В╨╡╨╣╨╜╨╡╤А╨┤╨╡)\n\n```css\n.container {\n  display: flex;\n\n  /* ╨С╨░╥У╤Л╤В */\n  flex-direction: row;          /* тЖТ ╨╛╥г╥У╨░ (╙Щ╨┤╨╡╨┐╨║╤Ц) */\n  flex-direction: column;       /* тЖУ ╤В╙й╨╝╨╡╨╜ */\n  flex-direction: row-reverse;  /* тЖР ╤Б╨╛╨╗╥У╨░ */\n\n  /* ╨Э╨╡╨│╤Ц╨╖╨│╤Ц ╨╛╤Б╤М╤В╨╡ ╤В╤Г╤А╨░╨╗╨░╤Г */\n  justify-content: flex-start;    /* ╤Б╨╛╨╗ ╨╢╨░╥Ы */\n  justify-content: center;        /* ╨╛╤А╤В╨░╥У╨░ */\n  justify-content: flex-end;      /* ╨╛╥г ╨╢╨░╥Ы */\n  justify-content: space-between; /* ╨░╤А╨░╤Б╤Л╨╜╨░ ╤В╨╡╥г ╨▒╙й╨╗╤Г */\n  justify-content: space-around;  /* ╨░╨╣╨╜╨░╨╗╨░╤Б╤Л╨╜╨░ ╤В╨╡╥г ╨▒╙й╨╗╤Г */\n\n  /* ╨Р╨╣╥Ы╨░╤Б ╨╛╤Б╤М╤В╨╡ ╤В╤Г╤А╨░╨╗╨░╤Г */\n  align-items: flex-start;  /* ╨╢╨╛╥У╨░╤А╤Л */\n  align-items: center;      /* ╨╛╤А╤В╨░╥У╨░ */\n  align-items: flex-end;    /* ╤В╙й╨╝╨╡╨╜ */\n  align-items: stretch;     /* ╤Б╨╛╨╖╤Г (╙Щ╨┤╨╡╨┐╨║╤Ц) */\n\n  /* ╨Ю╤А╨░╨╜╨░╨╗╨░╤Б╤Г */\n  flex-wrap: nowrap;    /* ╨▒╤Ц╤А ╨╢╨╛╨╗╨┤╨░ (╙Щ╨┤╨╡╨┐╨║╤Ц) */\n  flex-wrap: wrap;      /* ╨╛╤А╨░╨╣╨┤╤Л */\n\n  /* ╨н╨╗╨╡╨╝╨╡╨╜╤В╤В╨╡╤А ╨░╤А╨░╤Б╤Л╨╜╨┤╨░╥У╤Л ╨▒╨╛╤Б ╨╛╤А╤Л╨╜ */\n  gap: 16px;            /* ╨▒╨░╤А╨╗╤Л╥Ы ╨░╤А╨░╨┤╨░ */\n  gap: 8px 16px;        /* ╨╢╨╛╨╗ | ╨▒╨░╥У╨░╨╜ */\n}\n```\n\n## Flex ╤Н╨╗╨╡╨╝╨╡╨╜╤В╤В╨╡ (╨▒╨░╨╗╨░╨╗╨░╤А╨┤╨░)\n\n```css\n.item {\n  flex: 1;          /* ╥Ы╨░╨╗╥У╨░╨╜ ╨╛╤А╤Л╨╜╨┤╤Л ╤В╨╛╨╗╨░ */\n  flex: 2;          /* flex: 1 ╨▒╨╛╨╗╥У╨░╨╜╨┤╨░╨╜ 2 ╨╡╤Б╨╡ ╨║╨╡╥г */\n  flex: 0 0 200px;  /* ╙й╨╗╤И╨╡╨╝╤Ц╨╜ ╙й╨╖╨│╨╡╤А╤В╨┐╨╡, 200px ╨▒╨╛╨╗ */\n}\n```\n\n## ╨Ц╨╕╤Ц ╥Ы╨╛╨╗╨┤╨░╨╜╤Л╨╗╨░╤В╤Л╨╜ ╨┐╨░╤В╤В╨╡╤А╨╜\n\n```css\n/* ╨Ю╤А╤В╨░╥У╨░ ╤В╤Г╤А╨░╨╗╨░╤Г */\n.center-me {\n  display: flex;\n  justify-content: center;\n  align-items: center;\n}\n\n/* ╨Э╨░╨▓╨╕╨│╨░╤Ж╨╕╤П: ╨╗╨╛╨│╨╛ + ╤Б╤Ц╨╗╤В╨╡╨╝╨╡╨╗╨╡╤А */\n.nav {\n  display: flex;\n  justify-content: space-between;\n  align-items: center;\n}\n\n/* ╨Ъ╨░╤А╤В╨╛╤З╨║╨░ ╤В╨╛╤А╤Л */\n.grid {\n  display: flex;\n  flex-wrap: wrap;\n  gap: 24px;\n}\n.grid-item {\n  flex: 1 1 300px; /* min 300px, ╙й╤Б╨╡ ╨░╨╗╨░╨┤╤Л */\n}\n```\n\n## ╨Ю╨╣╤Л╨╜ ╨░╤А╥Ы╤Л╨╗╤Л ╥п╨╣╤А╨╡╨╜╤Г\n\n**Flexbox Froggy** ╨╛╨╣╤Л╨╜╤Л╨╜ ╨╛╨╣╨╜╨░╥г╤Л╨╖: https://flexboxfroggy.com/	\N	╨в╨░╨┐╤Б╤Л╤А╨╝╨░: Flex ╨║╨╛╨╜╤В╨╡╨╣╨╜╨╡╤А╤Ц╨╜╨┤╨╡ ╤Н╨╗╨╡╨╝╨╡╨╜╤В╤В╨╡╤А╨┤╤Ц ╤В╤Ц╨│╤Ц╨╜╨╡╨╜ ╨Ю╨а╨в╨Р╥Т╨Р ╤В╤Г╤А╨░╨╗╨░╨╣╤В╤Л╨╜ ╥Ы╨░╤Б╨╕╨╡╤В?\n\n.container {\n  display: flex;\n  ___: center;\n}\n\n╨в╨╡╨║ ╥Ы╨░╤Б╨╕╨╡╤В ╨░╤В╨░╤Г╤Л╨╜ ╨╢╨░╨╖╤Л╥г╤Л╨╖ (╨╢╨░╤Г╨░╨┐: align-items)	align-items	6	2026-03-03 20:34:17.921
0916a047-c38a-45ad-b789-bf2e725df453	ca86f924-9b0c-4b32-8ab3-6e18faf54a41	\N	Responsive Design: ╨╝╨╡╨┤╨╕╨░ ╤Б╥▒╤А╨░╤Г╨╗╨░╤А	# Responsive Design тАФ ╨С╨╡╨╣╤Ц╨╝╨┤╨╡╨╗╨╡╤В╤Ц╨╜ ╨Ф╨╕╨╖╨░╨╣╨╜\n\nResponsive ╨┤╨╕╨╖╨░╨╣╨╜ тАФ ╤Б╨░╨╣╤В╤Л╥г╤Л╨╖╨┤╤Л╥г ╨▒╨░╤А╨╗╤Л╥Ы ╤Г╤Б╤В╤А╨╛╨╣╤Б╤В╨▓╨╛╨┤╨░╤А╨┤╨░ (╤В╨╡╨╗╨╡╤Д╨╛╨╜, ╨┐╨╗╨░╨╜╤И╨╡╤В, ╨║╨╛╨╝╨┐╤М╤О╤В╨╡╤А) ╨╢╨░╥Ы╤Б╤Л ╨║╙й╤А╤Ц╨╜╤Г╤Ц╨╜ ╥Ы╨░╨╝╤В╨░╨╝╨░╤Б╤Л╨╖ ╨╡╤В╤Г.\n\n## Viewport Meta ╤В╨╡╨│╤Ц\n\n```html\n<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">\n```\n\n╨С╥▒╨╗ ╤В╨╡╨│╤Б╤Ц╨╖ ╨╝╨╛╨▒╨╕╨╗╨┤╤Ц ╨▒╤А╨░╤Г╨╖╨╡╤А╨╗╨╡╤А ╨▒╨╡╤В╤В╤Ц ╨║╤Ц╤И╤Ц╤А╨╡╨╣╨╝╨╡╨╣╨┤╤Ц!\n\n## Media Query ╤Б╨╕╨╜╤В╨░╨║╤Б╨╕╤Б╤Ц\n\n```css\n/* ╨Ь╨╛╨▒╨╕╨╗╨┤╤Ц: 0тАУ767px */\n@media (max-width: 767px) {\n  .container { padding: 16px; }\n  .nav { flex-direction: column; }\n}\n\n/* ╨Я╨╗╨░╨╜╤И╨╡╤В: 768тАУ1023px */\n@media (min-width: 768px) and (max-width: 1023px) {\n  .grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); }\n}\n\n/* ╨Ф╨╡╤Б╨║╤В╨╛╨┐: 1024px+ */\n@media (min-width: 1024px) {\n  .grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); }\n}\n```\n\n## Mobile First ╤В╙Щ╤Б╤Ц╨╗╤Ц (╥▒╤Б╤Л╨╜╤Л╨╗╨░╨┤╤Л)\n\n╨Р╨╗╨┤╤Л╨╝╨╡╨╜ ╨╝╨╛╨▒╨╕╨╗╨┤╤Ц ╤Б╤В╨╕╨╗╤М ╨╢╨░╨╖╤Л╥г╤Л╨╖, ╤Б╨╛╨┤╨░╨╜ ╨║╨╡╨╣╤Ц╨╜ ╥п╨╗╨║╨╡╨╜ ╤Н╨║╤А╨░╨╜╤Л ╥п╤И╤Ц╨╜ ╨║╨╡╥г╨╡╨╣╤В╤Ц╥г╤Ц╨╖:\n\n```css\n/* ╨Ь╨╛╨▒╨╕╨╗╨┤╤Ц (╨▒╨░╨╖╨░╨┤╨░╨╜) */\n.grid {\n  display: grid;\n  grid-template-columns: 1fr;\n  gap: 16px;\n}\n\n/* ╨Я╨╗╨░╨╜╤И╨╡╤В */\n@media (min-width: 768px) {\n  .grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); }\n}\n\n/* ╨Ф╨╡╤Б╨║╤В╨╛╨┐ */\n@media (min-width: 1200px) {\n  .grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); }\n}\n```\n\n## ╨Ц╨╕╤Ц ╥Ы╨╛╨╗╨┤╨░╨╜╤Л╨╗╨░╤В╤Л╨╜ Breakpoints\n\n| ╨Р╤В╨░╤Г╤Л | ╨Ъ╨╡╥г╨┤╤Ц╨║ |\n|-------|--------|\n| Mobile (xs) | < 576px |\n| Mobile (sm) | тЙе 576px |\n| Tablet (md) | тЙе 768px |\n| Laptop (lg) | тЙе 992px |\n| Desktop (xl) | тЙе 1200px |\n\n## ╨Я╨░╨╣╨┤╨░╨╗╤Л CSS ╨▒╤Ц╤А╨╗╤Ц╨║╤В╨╡╤А╤Ц\n\n```css\n/* ╨в╨╕╤П╨╜╨░╥Ы╤В╤Л ╨▒╤Ц╤А╨╗╤Ц╨║╤В╨╡╤А */\nwidth: 300px;      /* ╨┐╨╕╨║╤Б╨╡╨╗ */\nfont-size: 16px;\n\n/* ╨б╨░╨╗╤Л╤Б╤В╤Л╤А╨╝╨░╨╗╤Л ╨▒╤Ц╤А╨╗╤Ц╨║╤В╨╡╤А */\nwidth: 50%;        /* ╨░╤В╨░-╤Н╨╗╨╡╨╝╨╡╨╜╤В╤В╨╡╨╜ % */\nfont-size: 1.5rem; /* root font-size-╤В╨░╨╜ (1rem = 16px) */\nheight: 100vh;     /* viewport ╨▒╨╕╤Ц╨║╤В╤Ц╨│╤Ц */\nwidth: 100vw;      /* viewport ╨║╨╡╥г╨┤╤Ц╨│╤Ц */\n```	\N	╨в╨░╨┐╤Б╤Л╤А╨╝╨░: Mobile First ╤В╙Щ╤Б╤Ц╨╗╤Ц╨╜╨┤╨╡ ╨╝╨╛╨▒╨╕╨╗╨┤╤Ц ╤Б╤В╨╕╨╗╤М╨┤╨╡╨╜ ╨║╨╡╨╣╤Ц╨╜ ╥п╨╗╨║╨╡╨╜ ╤Н╨║rans ╥п╤И╤Ц╨╜ ╥Ы╨╛╨╗╨┤╨░╨╜╤Л╨╗╨░╤В╤Л╨╜ CSS ╤Б╨╕╨╜╤В╨░╨║╤Б╨╕╤Б╤Ц?\n\n╨в╨╡╨║ ╨╡╨║╤Ц ╤Б╙й╨╖╨┤╤Ц ╨╢╨░╨╖╤Л╥г╤Л╨╖ (╨╢╨░╤Г╨░╨┐: media query)	media query	8	2026-03-03 20:34:17.927
f7bfddd1-a294-40f7-a6da-84e7ca27b9d5	bf17e20f-c223-43aa-9fbc-ea992580373d	\N	JavaScript ╨╜╨╡╨╜╤Ц ╨▒╤Ц╨╗╨┤╤Ц╤А╨╡╨┤╤Ц? ╨С╤А╨░╤Г╨╖╨╡╤А╨┤╨╡ ╥Ы╨░╨╗╨░╨╣ ╤Ц╤Б╨║╨╡ ╥Ы╨╛╤Б╤Л╨╗╨░╨┤╤Л?	# JavaScript тАФ ╨Т╨╡╨▒ ╨▒╨╡╤В╤В╤Ц╥г ╨Ю╨╣╨╗╨░╤Г ╨Ь╥п╨╝╨║╤Ц╨╜╨┤╤Ц╨│╤Ц\n\nJavaScript (JS) тАФ ╨▒╤А╨░╤Г╨╖╨╡╤А╨┤╨╡ ╨╢╥▒╨╝╤Л╤Б ╤Ц╤Б╤В╨╡╨╣╤В╤Ц╨╜ ╨▒╨░╥У╨┤╨░╤А╨╗╨░╨╝╨░╨╗╨░╤Г ╤В╤Ц╨╗╤Ц. ╨Ю╨╗ ╨▓╨╡╨▒ ╨▒╨╡╤В╤В╨╡╤А╨│╨╡ ╙й╨╖╨░╤А╨░ ╔Щ╤А╨╡╨║╨╡╤В (╨╕╨╜╤В╨╡╤А╨░╨║╤В╨╕╨▓╤В╤Ц╨╗╤Ц╨║) ╨▒╨╡╤А╨╡╨┤╤Ц.\n\n## JavaScript ╨╜╨╡ ╨╢╨░╤Б╨░╨╣ ╨░╨╗╨░╨┤╤Л?\n\n- ╨С╨░╤В╤Л╤А╨╝╨░╨╗╨░╤А╥У╨░ ╨║╨╗╨╕╨║ ╙й╥г╨┤╨╡╤Г\n- ╨Ф╨╡╤А╨╡╨║╤В╨╡╤А╨┤╤Ц ╤В╨╡╨║╤Б╨╡╤А╤Г (╨▓╨░╨╗╨╕╨┤╨░╤Ж╨╕╤П)\n- ╨Р╨╜╨╕╨╝╨░╤Ж╨╕╤П ╨╢╨░╤Б╨░╤Г  \n- ╨б╨╡╤А╨▓╨╡╤А╨╝╨╡╨╜ ╨┤╨╡╤А╨╡╨║╤В╨╡╤А ╨░╨╗╨╝╨░╤Б╤Г (AJAX)\n- DOM (HTML) ╙й╨╖╨│╨╡╤А╤В╤Г\n- Cookie, localStorage ╨╢╥▒╨╝╤Л╤Б╤Л\n\n## ╨С╤А╨░╤Г╨╖╨╡╤А╨┤╨╡ ╤Ц╤Б╨║╨╡ ╥Ы╨╛╤Б╤Г\n\n### 1. HTML ╤Ц╤И╤Ц╨╜╨┤╨╡ (╨╢╤Л╨╗╨┤╨░╨╝ ╤В╨╡╨║╤Б╨╡╤А╤Г ╥п╤И╤Ц╨╜)\n```html\n<script>\n  alert("╨б╙Щ╨╗╨╡╨╝, JavaScript!");\n</script>\n```\n\n### 2. ╨б╤Л╤А╤В╥Ы╤Л ╤Д╨░╨╣╨╗ (╥▒╤Б╤Л╨╜╤Л╨╗╨░╨┤╤Л)\n```html\n<script src="app.js"></script>\n```\n\n### 3. Browser Console (F12 тЖТ Console)\n╨С╤А╨░╤Г╨╖╨╡╤А╨┤╨╡ F12 ╨▒╨░╤Б╤Л╥г╤Л╨╖ тЖТ Console ╥Ы╨╛╨╣╤Л╨╜╨┤╤Л╤Б╤Л тЖТ JS ╨║╨╛╨┤╤В╨░╤А╤Л╨╜ ╨╢╨░╨╖╤Г╥У╨░ ╨▒╨╛╨╗╨░╨┤╤Л.\n\n## ╨Р╨╗╥У╨░╤И╥Ы╤Л ╨▒╨░╥У╨┤╨░╤А╨╗╨░╨╝╨░\n\n```javascript\nconsole.log("╨б╙Щ╨╗╨╡╨╝, ╨Ф╥п╨╜╨╕╨╡!"); // Console-╥У╨░ ╤И╤Л╥У╨░╤А╤Г\nalert("╨б╙Щ╨╗╨╡╨╝!");              // ╨в╨╡╤А╨╡╨╖╨╡ ╤И╤Л╥У╨░╤А╤Г\nprompt("╨Р╤В╤Л╥г╤Л╨╖?");            // ╨Ф╨╡╤А╨╡╨║╤В╨╡╤А ╤Б╥▒╤А╨░╤В╤Г\n```\n\n## ╨Р╨╣╨╜╤Л╨╝╨░╨╗╤Л╨╗╨░╤А (Variables)\n\n```javascript\n// ╥Ъ╨░╨╖╤Ц╤А╨│╤Ц ╨╖╨░╨╝╨░╨╜╨░╤Г╨╕ ╨╢╨╛╨╗:\nlet age = 25;          // ╙й╨╖╨│╨╡╤А╤В╤Г╨│╨╡ ╨▒╨╛╨╗╨░╨┤╤Л\nconst name = "╨Р╨╗╨╕╨▒╨╡╨║"; // ╙й╨╖╨│╨╡╤А╤В╤Г╨│╨╡ ╨С╨Ю╨Ы╨Ь╨Р╨Щ╨Ф╨л\n\n// ╨Х╤Б╨║╤Ц ╨╢╨╛╨╗ (╨▒╨╛╨╗╨┤╤Л╤А╨╝╨░╥г╤Л╨╖):\nvar score = 100;       // ╨┐╤А╨╛╨▒╨╗╨╡╨╝╨░╨╗╤Л\n```\n\n## ╨Ф╨╡╤А╨╡╨║╤В╨╡╤А ╤В╥п╤А╨╗╨╡╤А╤Ц\n\n```javascript\nlet num    = 42;          // Number\nlet text   = "╨б╙Щ╨╗╨╡╨╝";    // String\nlet flag   = true;        // Boolean\nlet nothing = null;       // Null\nlet undef;                // Undefined\nlet obj    = {};           // Object\nlet arr    = [];           // Array (List)\n```\n\n## typeof ╨╛╨┐╨╡╤А╨░╤В╨╛╤А╤Л\n\n```javascript\nconsole.log(typeof 42);       // "number"\nconsole.log(typeof "hello");  // "string"\nconsole.log(typeof true);     // "boolean"\nconsole.log(typeof null);     // "object" (╨▒╥▒╨╗ JS-╤В╨╡╨│╤Ц ╨▒╨░╨│!)\n```	\N	╨в╨░╨┐╤Б╤Л╤А╨╝╨░: JavaScript-╤В╨╡ ╙й╨╖╨│╨╡╤А╤В╤Ц╨╗╨╝╨╡╨╣╤В╤Ц╨╜ (╨║╨╛╨╜╤Б╤В╨░╨╜╤В╨░) ╨░╨╣╨╜╤Л╨╝╨░╨╗╤Л ╨╢╨░╤А╨╕╤П╨╗╨░╨╣╤В╤Л╨╜ ╨║╤Ц╨╗╤В ╤Б╙й╨╖?\n\n╨в╨╡╨║ ╨║╤Ц╨╗╤В ╤Б╙й╨╖╨┤╤Ц ╨╢╨░╨╖╤Л╥г╤Л╨╖ (╨╢╨░╤Г╨░╨┐: const)	const	1	2026-03-03 20:34:17.941
ec9ea970-368c-446e-911d-ee9f10537aea	bf17e20f-c223-43aa-9fbc-ea992580373d	\N	╨Ю╨┐╨╡╤А╨░╤В╨╛╤А╨╗╨░╤А, ╤И╨░╤А╤В╤В╨░╤А, ╤Б╨░╨╗╤Л╤Б╤В╤Л╤А╤Г	# JavaScript ╨Ю╨┐╨╡╤А╨░╤В╨╛╤А╨╗╨░╤А & ╨и╨░╤А╤В╤В╨░╤А\n\n## ╨Р╤А╨╕╤Д╨╝╨╡╤В╨╕╨║╨░╨╗╤Л╥Ы ╨╛╨┐╨╡╤А╨░╤В╨╛╤А╨╗╨░╤А\n\n```javascript\nlet a = 10, b = 3;\nconsole.log(a + b);  // 13 тАФ ╥Ы╨╛╤Б╤Г\nconsole.log(a - b);  // 7  тАФ ╨░╨╗╤Г\nconsole.log(a * b);  // 30 тАФ ╨║╙й╨▒╨╡╨╣╤В╤Г\nconsole.log(a / b);  // 3.333... тАФ ╨▒╙й╨╗╤Г\nconsole.log(a % b);  // 1  тАФ ╥Ы╨░╨╗╨┤╤Л╥Ы (╨╝╨╛╨┤╤Г╨╗╤М)\nconsole.log(a ** b); // 1000 тАФ ╨┤╙Щ╤А╨╡╨╢╨╡ (10┬│)\n```\n\n## ╨б╨░╨╗╤Л╤Б╤В╤Л╤А╤Г ╨╛╨┐╨╡╤А╨░╤В╨╛╤А╨╗╨░╤А╤Л\n\n```javascript\nconsole.log(5 == "5");  // true  (╤В╨╡╨║ ╨╝╙Щ╨╜, ╨в╨Ш╨Я ╨в╨Х╨Ъ╨б╨Х╨а╨Ь╨Х╨Щ╨Ф╨Ж)\nconsole.log(5 === "5"); // false (╨╝╙Щ╨╜ + ╤В╨╕╨┐ тАФ ╥░╨б╨л╨Э╨л╨Ы╨Р╨Ф╨л!)\nconsole.log(5 != "5");  // false\nconsole.log(5 !== "5"); // true\nconsole.log(10 > 5);    // true\nconsole.log(10 >= 10);  // true\n```\n\n**╨Х╤А╨╡╨╢╨╡:** ╙Ш╤А╨┤╨░╨╣╤Л╨╝ `===` ╥Ы╨╛╨╗╨┤╨░╨╜╤Л╥г╤Л╨╖, `==` ╨╡╨╝╨╡╤Б!\n\n## ╨Ы╨╛╨│╨╕╨║╨░╨╗╤Л╥Ы ╨╛╨┐╨╡╤А╨░╤В╨╛╤А╨╗╨░╤А\n\n```javascript\n// && тАФ ╨Ц╙Ш╨Э╨Х (╨╡╨║╨╡╤Г╤Ц ╨┤╨╡ true ╨▒╨╛╨╗╤Г╤Л ╤В╨╕╤Ц╤Б)\nconsole.log(true && true);   // true\nconsole.log(true && false);  // false\n\n// || тАФ ╨Э╨Х╨Ь╨Х╨б╨Х (╨║╨╡╨╝ ╨┤╨╡╨│╨╡╨╜╨┤╨╡ ╨▒╤Ц╤А╤Ц true ╨▒╨╛╨╗╤Г╤Л ╤В╨╕╤Ц╤Б)\nconsole.log(false || true);  // true\nconsole.log(false || false); // false\n\n// ! тАФ ╨Ц╨Ю╥Ъ (╨╕╨╜╨▓╨╡╤А╤Б╨╕╤П)\nconsole.log(!true);   // false\nconsole.log(!false);  // true\n```\n\n## if/else ╤И╨░╤А╤В╤Л\n\n```javascript\nlet score = 75;\n\nif (score >= 90) {\n  console.log("╙и╤В╨╡ ╨╢╨░╥Ы╤Б╤Л!");\n} else if (score >= 70) {\n  console.log("╨Ц╨░╥Ы╤Б╤Л!");\n} else if (score >= 50) {\n  console.log("╥Ъ╨░╨╜╨░╥У╨░╤В╤В╨░╨╜╨░╤А╨╗╤Л╥Ы");\n} else {\n  console.log("╥Ъ╨░╨╣╤В╨░ ╤В╨░╨┐╤Б╤Л╤А╤Г ╨║╨╡╤А╨╡╨║");\n}\n```\n\n## ╨в╨╡╤А╨╜╨░╤А╨╗╤Л ╨╛╨┐╨╡╤А╨░╤В╨╛╤А (╥Ы╤Л╤Б╥Ы╨░ if)\n\n```javascript\n// ╨б╨╕╨╜╤В╨░╨║╤Б╨╕╤Б: ╤И╨░╤А╤В ? ╤И╤Л╨╜ ╨▒╨╛╨╗╤Б╨░ : ╨╢╨░╨╗╥У╨░╨╜ ╨▒╨╛╨╗╤Б╨░\nlet age = 20;\nlet status = age >= 18 ? "╨Ъ╙Щ╨╝╨╡╨╗╨╡╤В╨║╨╡ ╤В╨╛╨╗╥У╨░╨╜" : "╨Ъ╙Щ╨╝╨╡╨╗╨╡╤В╨║╨╡ ╤В╨╛╨╗╨╝╨░╥У╨░╨╜";\nconsole.log(status); // "╨Ъ╙Щ╨╝╨╡╨╗╨╡╤В╨║╨╡ ╤В╨╛╨╗╥У╨░╨╜"\n```\n\n## switch ╨╛╨┐╨╡╤А╨░╤В╨╛╤А╤Л\n\n```javascript\nlet day = "╨┤╥п╨╣╤Б╨╡╨╜╨▒╤Ц";\n\nswitch(day) {\n  case "╨┤╥п╨╣╤Б╨╡╨╜╨▒╤Ц":\n    console.log("╨Ц╥▒╨╝╤Л╤Б ╨║╥п╨╜╤Ц");\n    break;\n  case "╤Б╨╡╨╜╨▒╤Ц":\n  case "╨╢╨╡╨║╤Б╨╡╨╜╨▒╤Ц":\n    console.log("╨Ф╨╡╨╝╨░╨╗╤Л╤Б");\n    break;\n  default:\n    console.log("╨Ц╥▒╨╝╤Л╤Б ╨║╥п╨╜╤Ц");\n}\n```	\N	╨в╨░╨┐╤Б╤Л╤А╨╝╨░: JavaScript-╤В╨╡ ╨╝╙Щ╨╜ ╨╝╨╡╨╜ ╤В╨╕╨┐╤В╤Ц ╨С╨Ж╨а╨Ф╨Х╨Щ ╤В╨╡╨║╤Б╨╡╤А╨╡╤В╤Ц╨╜ ╨╛╨┐╨╡╤А╨░╤В╨╛╤А?\n\n╨в╨╡╨║ ╨╛╨┐╨╡╤А╨░╤В╨╛╤А╨┤╤Л ╨╢╨░╨╖╤Л╥г╤Л╨╖ (╨╢╨░╤Г╨░╨┐: ===)	===	2	2026-03-03 20:34:17.943
